  Ideapreneurship™
At HCL, innovation is not just another word, it’s part of our organizational heritage and DNA - a journey that began in 1976 and continues to power us ahead even today. The culture at HCL Technologies – ideapreneurship™ as we call it - makes the license to ideate a distinctive organizational capability. We see a grassroot movement that has rallied the entire organization behind this innovation agenda, in a manner that leads to relationships that deliver value beyond the contract to our customers. Read More    
     
  RELATIONSHIP BEYOND THE CONTRACT
In today's uncertain world, not even the best contract can capture what will change tomorrow. A contract can only convert to business advantage through a value centric relationship. Our belief in the values of trust, transparency, flexibility and value-centricity, fueled by our philosophy of 'Employees First', ensures the continued pursuit of our customers' best interests. Driven by our Mode 1-2-3 Strategy, we help clients reimagine their business in the digital age. This strategy is backed by the ‘Relationship Beyond the Contract’ promise of 115,000+ Ideapreneurs who chase a shared goal of improving our customers' business through everyday innovation and value addition through alignment to business needs. Read More    
     
  MODE 1-2-3 STRATEGY
Businesses across industries stand at an inflection point today. Far-reaching disruption fuelled by technologies like Digitalization, Analytics, Cloud, loT and Automation mean these technologies lie at the core of any enterprise that is trying to reinvent itself. As the demand for these services increase, HCL Technologies is accelerating its evolution into a next-generation technology services firm through our Mode 1-2-3 strategy. Read More       LEADERSHIPBOARD OF DIRECTORSEXECUTIVE PROFILES Shiv NadarFounder & Chairman - HCL, Shiv Nadar Foundation Roshni Nadar MalhotraExecutive Director & CEO, HCL Corporation | Director, HCL Technologies | Trustee, Shiv Nadar Foundation Robin AbramsDirector R. SrinivasanDirector Sosale Shankara SastryDirector Keki MistryDirector Subramanin MadhavanDirector Sudhindar Krishan KhannaDirector Thomas SieberDirector Nishi VasudevaDirector Deepak KapoorDirector C VijayakumarPresident & CEO, HCL Technologies Anil ChananaChief Financial Officer GH RaoPresident - Engineering and R&D Services (ERS) Rahul SinghPresident – Financial Services Ajit KumarPresident – Applications & SI Services Delivery Karan PuriSenior Corporate Vice President - Consumer and Commercial  Services, Americas Anand BirjeCorporate Vice President – Digital & Analytics Anoop TiwariCorporate Vice President – Business Services Anup Dutta Corporate Vice President – ERS Delivery (ECH, Hardware & VLSI) Apparao V VCorporate Vice President - Financial Services Delivery Arun PaiCorporate Vice President - Commercial Industries, Americas Ashish Kumar GuptaCorporate Vice President - ITO and Infrastructure Services Sales EMEA Jagadeshwar GattuCorporate Vice President - Infrastructure Delivery, Americas Jonathan HancockCorporate Vice President - Enterprise SI Delivery Maninder SinghCorporate Vice President - CyberSecurity Services Sukamal BanerjeeCorporate Vice President - ERS Sales (Hi Tech & Comm), Head - IoT WoRKS Vijay Anand Guntur Corporate Vice President - ERS PTS & SDES Vikram